        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 1 at 5:18PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 518 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Black Butte Ranch, or 23 miles west of Redmond, moving northeast at 5
mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Sisters, Black Butte Ranch, and Camp Sherman.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
